{"tid":2399938,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[捍衛粵語 最佳示範] 好懷念！曾經嘅Online Game香港官網係可以「粵語入文」","createTime":"2021-02-08T13:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T13:54:14.000Z","uid":109923,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b44a2208e6ca7d862dccf217fd7cb412e1b22886","tid":2399938,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"無聊睇返以前啲OLG官網，發現卡巴拉島個香港官網好有heart，直接粵語入文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxWyHZF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxWyHZF.png&h=c7fd51a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活動期間：唔定時<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8SJ5dC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8SJ5dC.png&h=353154ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n技能說明都係粵文，一切都係咁親切，一啲都唔突兀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3jbfbUr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3jbfbUr.png&h=b49289a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時，日本、韓國、越南，都係以漢字嚟書寫佢哋嘅語言<br />\n到咗而家，日本係假名漢字混用，韓國就用諺文，而越南就拉丁化<br />\n<br />\n韓國係支那鄰近小國當中，最成功逃離&quot;被中國人&quot;命運的國家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cuPaGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cuPaGS</a><br />\n上面個post都講過，要保護到自己嘅語言，最需要嘅就係有「展示到自己語言特色」嘅文字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於韓文廢除漢字要靠grammar(黏著語)同近代大量引入英文外來詞，而粵文係做唔到，所以絕不建議直接將漢字拉丁拼音化<br />\n<br />\n事實上，香港只需要「粵語入文+外來詞」都足以自成一系<br />\n「巴士、的士」唔好再聽中小學老師講，要改成書面語嘅「公車、計程車」<br />\n「朱古力」就係「朱古力」，唔係「巧克力」<br />\n「雪糕」就係「雪糕」，唔係「冰淇淋」<br />\n咩書面語、口語之分只係大中華膠消滅粵語嘅手段<br />\n<br />\n香港要捍衛粵語只需要宣揚「粤語入文」、將「粤文規範化」、「英文、日文來詞規範化」<br />\n隨住科技發展，新事物多數由西方引入，文化亦持續受西方、日本影響，香港應該引入更多「英文、日文外來詞」嚟發展自己嘅書寫系統<br />\n正如一百年前，現代漢語由日文引入好多詞語一樣，我哋依家用緊嘅哲學、民主、藝術、健康、社會、革命、科學、電話、經濟、警察、雜誌、邏輯都係日本人翻譯<br />\n「democracy」以前係叫「德謨克拉西」而唔係「民主」<br />\n<br />\n學校教育已經俾中共同港共限定咗，所以...<br />\n做marketing嘅朋友，多啲用「粤文」做宣傳！<br />\n做PR/CS嘅朋友，多啲用「粤文」回覆查詢！<br />\n經營youtube嘅朋友，多啲用「粤文」做標題&amp;description！<br />\n我哋要俾學生知道，出咗社會就係粵文嘅世界"},{"pid":"effdedec85869bec8754f80efefc9c3fe23b9c89","tid":2399938,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"2002年嘅瑪奇官網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />需要用flash player先睇到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/544XqyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F544XqyX.png&h=d68c53e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年封測嘅擷圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rPnmSfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPnmSfS.jpg&h=abe5a128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bzvok9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzvok9c.jpg&h=8868f59a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFsNNPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFsNNPc.jpg&h=f663d3e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pOhqAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pOhqAS.jpg&h=e7b7ded3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ao1ZDVS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAo1ZDVS.jpg&h=f8a639fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"497489281850257d626adab34c02325180c7c280","tid":2399938,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:04:41.000Z","msg":"20年前嘅影片resolution<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲download到嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSwyJoX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSwyJoX.png&h=fd07bbc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffc375c5baea40bf5d6671bd3ff9a7664e7ffb88","tid":2399938,"uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021